Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,# Regality 君音
Comment: 0,0:01:21.91,0:01:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,## 對話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.91,0:01:26.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}但，我們可以直接跟他們買蛋糕，不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.25,0:01:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}是「可以」。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.25,0:01:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}但那我們就少了「一起烤蛋糕」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.18,0:01:34.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}外加我花在給他們拍馬屁，就為了那死配方，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.18,0:01:36.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}一直苦苦求他們花的功夫，全都會付諸流水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.05,0:01:39.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}而且我們說好了要「做」蛋糕，不是「買」蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.81,0:01:43.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}而廣大神通的 Trixie 最討厭食言！
Comment: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,# Mad This Time 發飆
Comment: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,## 前奏
Comment: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.45,0:01:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}有什麼正在空氣中點燃\NSomething's burning in the air tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.35,0:01:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}你鼻樑抬高，繼續放風箏\Nyou turn your nose up, just keep flying that kite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:01:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}沒事沒事沒事我沒事\NI'm fine I'm fine I'm fine I'm fine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:02:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}就算我跟你實說，你也會發飆\Nand if I told you, you'd be mad this time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我都在約談我同類\NI've counseled all the ones like me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.38,0:02:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}就在友誼學校，聽過沒\Nin the school of friendship, honestly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:08.25,Special-1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(854,1022)}去過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:08.98,Special-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1050,994)}做過
