Comment: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,## 導歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我早就在這著地獄生存\NI've been living in this hell already
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我就是又個標把，步槍拿穩\NI'm just another target, hold and steady
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我一直以來都自己一人\NI've been living on my own since then
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.31,0:02:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我就是遊民，直到他們接管\NI'm nomadic as they come take ten
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我是如此廣大神通\NI'm so great and powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我想你們都有聽過\NI've bet you heard it all before
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}但我需要一直說\NI need to repeat myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}一直沒進你耳朵\Nyou weren't listening till now
Comment: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,## 副歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}你這次會發飆\NYou'll be mad this time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}會發飆\NMad this time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}會發飆\NMad this time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}你想我想我知你知\NYou think I think I know you know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}你說你想你是最棒\Nyou said you think you're the best
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我更明白\NI know better
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.21,0:03:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}你會發飆發飆發飆發飆\NYou'll be mad mad mad mad mad mad mad
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.98,0:03:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}當我知道我朋友有誰\Nwhen I know who my friends are
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}在你奪走一切之前\NDidn't know what I wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我都不知道想要啥\Ntill you took it all away
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}而現在我只想要\NNow the only thing I want
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}度過每一天\Nis to live another day
