Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}但心底，他們從未忘記\Nbut deep down they never forget
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}畢竟傷口這麼深\NWhen the scars cut deep like that
