Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}只要我保持好，但老實說，遲早\Nif I do my best, or rather, "when"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我給你行禮但我懶得管你\NI tip my hat to you but I couldn't care less
